node.text:
❤️Absolutely ADDICTIVE snacks from @crustyssg that is perfect for munching during this Circuit Breaker period! ⁣
⁣
👍🏻Soyskin Crisps with real Salted egg- vegetarian mock goose chips that are made of crispy rolled bean curd skin. This was my favourite and soo good!!!! ❤️❤️⁣
⁣
👍🏻Chilli Crab Popcorn- premium grade non-GMO corn kernels made with quality flavourful spices. Popping goodness!⁣
⁣
👍🏻Salted Egg Fish Skins- I don’t think anyone can miss hearing me munching these away! Super crispy!⁣
⁣
These snacks are available at @fairpricesg @watsonssg @cheers_sg @qoo10sg @lazada_sg @shopee_sg and all petrol stations! Hurry get yours to munch! Thank you @crustyssg for the yummies!⁣
⁣
